column18: 02/07/2014: Assailants set fire to a Kentucky Fried Chicken (KFC) restaurant in Upper Hutt city, Wellington region, New Zealand. There were no injuries in the attack; however, the building was badly damaged by the fire. The Animal Liberation Front (ALF) claimed responsibility for the incident in a post online.
column108: A Kentucky Fried Chicken restaurant was damaged in this attack.
